name: TheDigitalCube
tag_list: web-design-singapore, web-development-singapore, seo-services, sem-campaigns, email-templates, website-optimization, digital-marketing-consultancy
overview:
TheDigitalCube provides web design, web development and SEO services in Singapore and South-East Asia.

The core values of the company are customized services, complete web solutions and focus on high quality, especially for designs. The people behind TheDigitalCube have more than 10 years of experience in designing and developping websites. TheDigitalCube provides other web solutions such as: sem campaigns, email template, website optimization, digital marketing consultancy, web hosting and mobile applications.

TheDigitalCube proposes packages for HTML websites, CMS based websites and eCommerce solutions with mobile application.

TheDigitalCube differentiates from other companies by the number of included options in all the packages: web hosting possibilities, enhanced Search Engine Optimization, favicon, valid HTML5 coding, secure solutions, speed enhancement and QR codes.
